\v 1 我​<a name="02601000100004" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">观看</a>​，​看​哪​，​在​<a name="02601000100014" ll="SDBH:רָקִיעַ:000000">穹苍</a>​之中​，​也​就​是​<a name="02601000100024" ll="SDBH:כְּרוּב:000000">基路伯</a>​的​<a name="02601000100020" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">头</a>​上​，​有​<a name="02601000100028;02601000100030" ll="SDBH:אֶבֶן:000008;SDBH:סַפִּיר:000000">蓝宝石</a>​的​形状​，​<a name="02601000100034" ll="SDBH:מַרְאֶה:000000">仿佛</a>​<a name="02601000100038" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000000">宝座</a>​的​<a name="02601000100036" ll="SDBH:דְּמוּת:000000">形像</a>​<a name="02601000100040" ll="SDBH:ראה:000001">显</a>​在​他们​上面​。 
\v 2 耶和华​对​那​<a name="02601000200012">身穿</a>​<a name="02601000200016" ll="SDBH:בַּד:000000">细麻</a>​<a name="02601000200016" ll="SDBH:בַּד:000000">衣</a>​<a name="02601000200012">的</a>​<a name="02601000200010">人</a>​<a name="02601000200004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">说</a>​：​“​你​<a name="02601000200022">进到</a>​<a name="02601000200042" ll="SDBH:כְּרוּב:000000" il="Ezekiel;Ezekiel_Calling;Ezekiel_vision;LivingCreatures-Facundus;LlivingCreatures-Manchester;NBGlo20140708;Nimrud, ivory sphinx" tl="HOTTP3679">基路伯</a>​下面​<a name="02601000200032" ll="SDBH:גַּלְגַּל:000000">旋转</a>​<a name="02601000200032" ll="SDBH:גַּלְגַּל:000000">的</a>​<a name="02601000200032" ll="SDBH:גַּלְגַּל:000000">轮子</a>​中​，​从​<a name="02601000200062" ll="SDBH:כְּרוּב:000000">基路伯</a>​之间​取出​<a name="02601000200050;02601000200052" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000">火炭</a>​<a name="02601000200046" ll="SDBH:מלא:000002">装满</a>​两​<a name="02601000200048" ll="SDBH:חֹפֶן:000000">手掌</a>​，​<a name="02601000200066" ll="SDBH:זרק:000000">撒</a>​在​<a name="02601000200072" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">城</a>​上​。​”​我​<a name="02601000200080" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">亲眼</a>​看见​他​<a name="02601000200076">进去</a>​。 
\v 3 那​<a name="02601000300026">人</a>​<a name="02601000300022">进去</a>​的​时候​，​<a name="02601000300006" ll="SDBH:כְּרוּב:000000">基路伯</a>​<a name="02601000300008">站</a>​在​<a name="02601000300018" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000">殿</a>​的​<a name="02601000300012" ll="SDBH:יָמִין:000000">南边</a>​，​<a name="02601000300032" ll="SDBH:עָנָן:000000">云彩</a>​<a name="02601000300034" ll="SDBH:מלא:000001">充满</a>​了​<a name="02601000300040;02601000300044" ll="SDBH:חָצֵר:000001">内院</a>​。 
