\v 7 这​<a name="02604100700008">围绕</a>​着​<a name="02604100700030" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917;Realia:3.14.1c;Realia:3.14.1e" tl="HOTTP3945">殿</a>​的​<a name="02604100700022" ll="SDBH:צֵלָע:000002">厢房</a>​越​<a name="02604100700012" ll="SDBH:מַעַל:001000">高</a>​越​<a name="02604100700004" ll="SDBH:רחב:000000">宽</a>​；​厢房​<a name="02604100700026" ll="SDBH:מוּסָב:000000" tl="HOTTP3945">围</a>​<a name="02604100700026" ll="SDBH:מוּסָב:000000" tl="HOTTP3945">着</a>​<a name="02604100700048" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000">殿</a>​<a name="02604100700034;02604100700038" ll="SDBH:מַעַל:001000">悬叠而上</a>​，​<a name="02604100700052">所以</a>​越​<a name="02604100700064" ll="SDBH:מַעַל:001000" tl="HOTTP3946">上面</a>​越​<a name="02604100700054" ll="SDBH:רֹחַב:000000" tl="HOTTP3946">宽</a>​，​从​<a name="02604100700072" ll="SDBH:תַּחְתֹּון:000000">下</a>​一​层​，​到​<a name="02604100700086" ll="SDBH:תִּיכֹון:000000">中</a>​一​层​，​到​<a name="02604100700080" ll="SDBH:עֶלְיֹון:000000">上</a>​一​层​。 
\v 8 我​又​<a name="02604100800004" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">见</a>​有​<a name="02604100800012" ll="SDBH:גֹּבַהּ:000000">高台</a>​<a name="02604100800014;02604100800016" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">围绕</a>​<a name="02604100800014;02604100800016" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">着</a>​<a name="02604100800010" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000">殿</a>​，​作为​<a name="02604100800024" ll="SDBH:צֵלָע:000002">厢房</a>​的​<a name="02604100800020" ll="SDBH:מוּסָדָה:000000">根基</a>​，​<a name="02604100800026" ll="SDBH:מְלֹא:000002">高</a>​足足​有​一​<a name="02604100800030" ll="SDBH:קָנֶה:000002">竿</a>​，​就​是​<a name="02604100800032" ll="SDBH:שֵׁשׁ:000000">六</a>​大​<a name="02604100800034" ll="SDBH:אַמָּה:000000">肘</a>​。 
\v 11 <a name="02604101100008" ll="SDBH:צֵלָע:000002">厢房</a>​的​<a name="02604101100004" ll="SDBH:פֶּתַח:000000">门口</a>​向着​<a name="02604101100014" ll="SDBH:נוח:000002">空地</a>​：​<a name="02604101100018" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">一</a>​<a name="02604101100016" ll="SDBH:פֶּתַח:000000">门</a>​<a name="02604101100020" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000006">向</a>​<a name="02604101100024" ll="SDBH:צָפֹון:000001">北</a>​，​<a name="02604101100030" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">一</a>​<a name="02604101100028" ll="SDBH:פֶּתַח:000000">门</a>​向​<a name="02604101100036" ll="SDBH:דָּרֹום:000000">南</a>​。​<a name="02604101100052;02604101100054" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">周围</a>​<a name="02604101100052;02604101100054" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">的</a>​<a name="02604101100042;02604101100046" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">空地</a>​<a name="02604101100040" ll="SDBH:רֹחַב:000000">宽</a>​<a name="02604101100048" ll="SDBH:חָמֵשׁ:000000">五</a>​<a name="02604101100050" ll="SDBH:אַמָּה:000000">肘</a>​。
    
